{"tid":1932751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外務省稱日本人因武漢新冠肺炎疫情在多國遭遇歧視","createTime":"2020-03-19T02:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T02:37:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa7985debed677b7bbdd1820d9862594e79c0b4","tid":1932751,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"日本外務省在18日的眾院外務委員會會議上就新型冠狀病毒疫情透露，日本人在德國、印度尼西亞等多個國家遭遇歧視。外相茂木敏充表示：&ldquo;從保護日僑的觀點出發，這也是極為重要的問題。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  在會議上，外務省領事局長水島光一介紹稱：&ldquo;在部分國家出現了對日本人的歧視性對待。&rdquo;作為具體例子，他提及在德國觀看足球比賽的日本遊客被趕出賽場一事。茂木指出，日本人在印尼遭遇歧視性言行。<br />\n<br />\n  關於在德國和印尼發生的問題，外務省表示已向對方國家政府和相關團體&ldquo;要求防止再次發生&rdquo;（茂木語）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/21db45cb0b3d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F21db45cb0b3d.html&d=AthmRk%2BBSDjaWf6zT95BzLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=abd2991a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/21db45cb0b3d.html</a>"},{"pid":"072f212bfc4ed9e33a8e4bfac62cdd60a46a7c8c","tid":1932751,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"你日本自己都歧視自己啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot202020-03-0420at206.03.2520PM20copy_qwo3o_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot202020-03-0420at206.03.2520PM20copy_qwo3o_1200x0.png&h=453bc1f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/radoIXXxWmM7nhHb2jBZPg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM4/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/5afc2dc90eacb418e05cf8bae6f3d467\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FradoIXXxWmM7nhHb2jBZPg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9NjM4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F